idi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-weight:\\r\\nbold\\\">This needs to be cited and it should be changed to look like the below:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nArial;color:#7030A0\\\">Current thinking, based on research, supports the view\\r\\nthat parental involvement\\u2026<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nArial;color:#7030A0\\\">(Kay 2005)<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">OR<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nArial;color:#7030A0\\\">As Kay (2005, p.5) said, \\u2018Current thinking, based on\\r\\nresearch, supports the view that parental involvement\\u2026\\u2019 we are now lead to\\r\\nbelieve\\u2026<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><div style=\\\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\\r\\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .75pt;padding:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm\\\">\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none;border:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:\\r\\nsolid windowtext .75pt;padding:0cm;mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\r\\n&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#7030A0\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/div><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nArial;color:#7030A0\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:red;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\\\">How are sources referenced in the main\\r\\ntext of the answer?<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraph\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\\r\\nmso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\\r\\nnone\\\"><b><i><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/i><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">If\\r\\nyou are using direct quotes from sources or writing other peoples\\u2019 ideas in your\\r\\nown words, you need to give their surname and date in the main body of the\\r\\nreport.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\\\">Example:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/b><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:#7030A0\\\">Smith (2010) suggested that etc....<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font