(56, 28, 82, '{\"Message\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" align=\\\"center\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\\r\\ntext-align:center;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\\r\\nnone\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\r\\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\\\">Referencing<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:\\r\\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-weight:\\r\\nbold\\\">In order to successfully complete you course, you must ensure that your\\r\\nwork is correctly referenced throughout!<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:#C10000\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\\r\\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">Referencing is a simple practice that you the learner must\\r\\ncomplete when producing your activities for this course. When completing your assessments,\\r\\nalthough for the most part you should answer in your own words from what you\\r\\nhave learnt and your own experiences, you will also be expected to refer to\\r\\nknowledge found in academic texts (where relevant), to back up your arguments.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><div style=\\\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\\r\\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .75pt;padding:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm\\\">\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\\r\\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none;\\r\\nborder:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .75pt;padding:0cm;\\r\\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/div><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\\r\\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\\r\\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\r\\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\\\">How to Reference<\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:white\\\"><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:white\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">When\\r\\ncompleting assignment questions, it is important that any quotations or material\\r\\nproduced by others that you<b> <\\/b>use\\r\\ninclude in your answer, are <\\/span><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\r\\n&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018cited\\u2019 <\\/span><\\/b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">and included in a <\\/span><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\r\\nfont-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018bibliography\\u2019<\\/span><\\/b><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">. <\\/span><\\/b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">This is to ensure that others reading\\r\\nyour text can find the original source and more importantly to show that the\\r\\nquoted material is originally produced by someone else and is not your own.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\\r\\ncolor:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018Citing\\u2019<\\/span><\\/b><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"> <\\/span><\\/b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">is simple enough to complete but is very important. It is\\r\\nbasically an acknowledgement of who wrote the material you are including (the\\r\\nauthor) and what year the book was published (date). NOTE: Only the authors\\r\\nsurname needs to be used.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">Citing\\r\\nshould be included appropriately at some point in the quote that you are using\\r\\nat either the beginning or end of the quote would be most logical. <o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">Cited\\r\\nquotes, need to also make up part of your bibliography, which is explained in a\\r\\nmoment.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\r\\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#7030A0\\\"><o:p><span style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\r\\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#7030A0\\\">For example:<\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\">You may decide to include the following quote you\\r\\nhave found in a book:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nArial;color:#7030A0\\\">Current thinking, based on research, supports the view\\r\\nthat parental involvement\\u2026<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:\\r\\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-b