(71, 28, 81, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hello Charlotte<\\/p><p>Thank you for replying to my email<\\/p><p>I hope that you had a wonderful Christmas and New Year<\\/p><p>I am sorry to hear about your family illness, and I know childcare is always an issue<\\/p><p>I am sure that your previous background in the early years sector, will help you to understand your units more clearly and certainly your Level 1 qualifications will also help with your knowledge and understanding for these units of work&nbsp;<\\/p><p>I am about to send you some emails, which have advice notes attached to them.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Please take your time to read through them, as I am sure they will help you with your studies and coursework.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">I am here to help you, so please do not hesitate to contact me if you need any help<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Bye for now<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Linda&nbsp;<br><\\/span><br><\\/p>\"}', 1515067450, 1, 0, 0);
