(83, 68, 40, '{\"Message\":\"<p>hi Samantha my name is Zac.<\\/p><p>I\'m sorry i haven\'t sent in any work yet it had been hectic as i work in a hotel on the bar and its been so busy! i have finished activity one but i don\'t know if it is long enough, i haven\'t written it as an essay form but then i feel i have included enough points, how do i go about sending it to you?<\\/p><p>Zac<\\/p>\"}', 1515338398, 1, 0, 0),
(84, 45, 28, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Dear Linda<\\/p><p>Merry Christmas and happy new Year to you and your family. As you can tell that i did not have time to do any studies but now that things have settled,<\\/p><p>I will concentrate on this course and read carefully your comment to improve myself to pass this new challenge.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\"><br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Kind Regards<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">King Yip<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">P.S. You can call me Peter.&nbsp;<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\"}', 1515394274, 1, 0, 0),
(85, 70, 29, '{\"Is your enquiry related to your course:\":\"<a href=\\\"\\/student\\/course\\/20\\\">Yes<\\/a>\",\"Is your enquiry related to one of your modules:\":\"Yes\",\"Which module:\":\"Module Two - Case Study 1 \\u2013 The Bodies in the Stream (The Jigsaw Case)\",\"Which of the following does this relate to:\":\"Underpinning Knowledge\",\"Message\":\"Hello, I am struggling to find a 5th specialist for activity 2? I have Pathologist, Anthropologist, Criminalistics and Anatomy so far.\"}', 1515399521, 1, 0, 0),
(86, 29, 70, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hi Emily,<\\/p><p>Think about the psychological side of things....does anything come to mind if you consider that aspect of it?<\\/p><p>Kind regards,<\\/p><p>Amanda&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', 1515399597, 1, 0, 0),
(87, 70, 29, '{\"Message\":\"<p>I\'ve been having a total mind block about the whole thing for about 2 weeks now and the only thing i can find is that the killer was only convicted because the judge and jury were impressed at how the case had been carried out.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 1515400768, 1, 0, 0),
(88, 29, 70, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Have you tried thinking about actual individuals who were involved in the case and what they brought? For example:<\\/p><p>*Sergeant Sloane<\\/p><p>*Dr Mearns<\\/p><p>*Professor Glaister<\\/p><p>These individuals all brought something to the evidence that came up - once you can work out what this was, you should be able to sort activity two out quite easily.<\\/p><p>As for your question where you are having a mind block - is this related to the same question?<\\/p><p>Kind regards,<\\/p><p>Amanda&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', 1515401202, 1, 0, 0),
(89, 70, 29, '{\"Message\":\"<p>I think i have figured it out, thank you.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Yes the mind-block was about the same thing.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Emily&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', 1515401556, 1, 0, 0),
(90, 29, 70, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Great - do let me know if you need anything else.<\\/p><p>Kind regards,<\\/p><p>Amanda&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', 1515401781, 1, 0, 0),
(91, 28, 45, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hello Peter<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>..... and a Happy New Year to you too<\\/p><p>I hope you enjoy your studies, and please do not forget to ask me if you need any help at all<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Bye for now<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Linda<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 1515417906, 1, 0, 0),
(92, 28, 52, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hello Marinela<\\/p><p>Happy New Year to you<\\/p><p>I hope you had a wonderful break<\\/p><p>I have not yet had a reply from you regarding the information I need from the welcome email<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">I will now send you another, please can you reply to this email as soon as possible.&nbsp; I am concerned that the emails may not be getting through to you&nbsp;<\\/span><br><\\/p><p>Regards<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Linda&nbsp;<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 1515418491, 0, 0, 0);
