(93, 28, 45, '{\"Message\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Hello<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">My name\\r\\nis&nbsp;<b>Linda Broome-Smith<\\/b>, and I have been allocated as your tutor.&nbsp; Please allow me to introduce myself to you.<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">I have\\r\\nworked in the childcare sector for many years.&nbsp; I have managed my own\\r\\npreschool, worked as a childminder and also worked in full day care nurseries,\\r\\nand schools throughout my career.<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">As a tutor\\r\\nand an assessor, I have taught a range of different levels and types of child\\r\\ncare and supporting teaching and learning in schools courses, both in the\\r\\nclassroom and on line.&nbsp; I have also\\r\\ntaught a range of management and leadership courses, in order to help others to\\r\\npossess the relevant skills to both effectively manage people and business\\r\\nmatters. <o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 7.5pt;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; back