(114, 29, 121, '{\"Message\":\"<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(52, 52, 52);\\\">Hi Vikki,<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(52, 52, 52);\\\">I am afraid that I don\'t have electronic access to do this so you will need to check with the office. Something that should be brought to their attention unless the two are meant to be the same? I can\'t tell as I receive the course in a different format I\'m afraid.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(52, 52, 52);\\\"><br><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(52, 52, 52);\\\">Kind regards,<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(52, 52, 52);\\\">Amanda<\\/p>\"}', 1515916611, 1, 0, 0),
(115, 128, 28, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hi Linda!&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Thank you for your kind email.&nbsp; I am an older student (46 years) and have 2 Special Needs kids (Autistic\\/ADHD - boy 13 was diagnosed at the age of 4, and a daughter 11 who has global learning delay for which I am in the process of applying for a statement.&nbsp; They both are at mainstream school.&nbsp; I am also recently divorced, a single mother, so hence I am looking for something that will fit around the children.&nbsp; I feel, that the practical experience I have will hopefully be transferable to other like children, hence I am doing the course.&nbsp; I hope to be able to give back my learning back to the Educational community.&nbsp; I am starting with Unit 1, as I thought it would be better to start from the beginning!..&nbsp;<\\/p><p>I do have a question, - is there any way I can get a the units in way of a paper pack?&nbsp; I know this is an online course, however it would be useful to actual refer to the hardcopies.&nbsp; And my head\\/eyes are starting to hurt, even with glasses!. My printer is not working at the moment and it will be expensive to goto the library or such to print each page(I am on benefits) - There is about 90 pages!&nbsp; The tables at the end are not clear enough - I am not able view the tables in one page, especially page 42.<\\/p><p>Thanks in advance&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Kindest regards<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Neeta<br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 1515969222, 1, 0, 0),
(116, 121, 29, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Good Morning Amanda<\\/p><p>Thank you for replying, i emailed the main office and they have sorted it for me, so i now have the correct module information for module 8<\\/p><p>Regards<\\/p><p>Vikki<br><\\/p>\"}', 1516003410, 1, 0, 0),
