(271, 28, 179, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hello Jade<\\/p><p>I have just sent you some advice sheets, which may be of use to you in your studies.<\\/p><p>An advice sheet to help you with referencing and creating a bibliography (this should be submitted as the last page of your work)<\\/p><p>An advice sheet to help you read and answer your questions effectively<\\/p><p>An advice sheet with a Glossary of Terms, so that you can understand the way the question has asked for an answer<\\/p><p>And an advice sheet so that you can see clearly the information on your feedback forms<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Bye for now<\\/p><p>Regards<\\/p><p>Linda<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 1517664043, 1, 0, 0),
