(273, 186, 65, '{\"Message\":\"<p>I have t deceived them Stonebridge deceived me I find you very rude I am dyslexic and some of your comments are s rude I am disgusted n made a formal complaint n now your accusing me of deceiving my employer I\\u2019ve spent 4000 down courses to be deceived I will not be continuing with you th No you need look at how your talks no t people as people have disabilities&nbsp;<\\/p><p>clearly you don\\u2019t take that into account!!!! Oh by the way I\\u2019ve sent your feedback to newspapers to publish Monday bout discriminating against disabilities&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', 1517717952, 1, 0, 0),
