(277, 81, 28, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hello Linda<\\/p><p>Sorry i didn\'t realise all 3 courses weren\'t with you, am i just completeing&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lms.ncchomelearning.co.uk\\/student\\/course\\/92\\\" style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 130, 198, 0.498039); position: relative; top: -1px; font-size: 15px;\\\">Supporting Teaching and Learning In Schools Award Level 3<\\/a>&nbsp;course for you? I\'m just confused because all three courses have been sent over together.<\\/p><p>Thank you for letting me know.<\\/p><p>Once all completed and hopefully passed :) will my&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lms.ncchomelearning.co.uk\\/student\\/course\\/92\\\" style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 130, 198, 0.498039); position: relative; top: -1px; font-size: 15px;\\\">Supporting Teaching and Learning In Schools Award Level 3<\\/a>&nbsp;certificate be sent by you?<\\/p><p>Many thanks&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Charlotte.<\\/p>\"}', 1517739383, 1, 0, 0),
