(279, 189, 28, '{\"Message\":\"<p><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">Hi Linda,<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">I have not had any&nbsp;experience within a childcare or education sector since I have left school. I am starting with&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lms.ncchomelearning.co.uk\\/student\\/course\\/92\\\" style=\\\"border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 130, 198, 0.498039); position: relative; top: -1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Supporting Teaching and Learning In Schools Award Level 3<\\/a>.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">I am&nbsp;currently working as an Office Junior, &nbsp;but have&nbsp;recently decided that I would like to become involved in teaching.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p>Kind regards,<\\/p><p>Abbie&nbsp;<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\"}', 1517776348, 1, 0, 0),
(280, 65, 186, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Dear Katie,<\\/p><p>I have just read through all of our emails and fail to see where or how I have been rude or insulting in any way.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Furthermore, I find your inference that I am in anyway derogatory towards anybody with extra needs not only unfounded and offensive, but potentially defamatory, as my impeccable history of working with people with extra needs bears testament.<\\/p><p>You told me that your employer thinks you have a level 3 qualification and you do not. Therefore, you have deceived your boss and should not be left alone with children by law. I am sorry that you find what I have said offensive, I am, however, just stating the facts that you gave me.<\\/p><p>Regards<\\/p><p>Sarah<br><\\/p>\"}', 1517778944, 0, 0, 0),
(281, 30, 99, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hi Ross,<br>I am terribly sorry for my delay in replying to your message. I did not get an email notification to say you had sent one and have only logged in today to check something and found it. I have flagged this up with NCC and I\'ll be aware that this can happen now and will check periodically.<br>You may have made some progress since you sent the message. You haven\'t said which essay you are attempting so I\'ll assume it\'s the first from what you\'ve said. In either then bear in mind the key points and aims and objectives of the module. You have to express your own opinion from what you have read. There is no right or wrong answer but you do have to explain why you have formed the opinion you have based on reference to the information in the module. <br>This is your first module and I will offer advice and suggestions for improvement in my feedback when you submit it either for future reference for future modules, or if needs be, if you are required to resubmit your essay. Please don\'t be worried and give it your best effort and we can take it from there.<br>Kind regards<br>Lucy <br><\\/p>\"}', 1517831694, 0, 0, 0),
