(286, 28, 189, '{\"Message\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" align=\\\"center\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">Glossary\\r\\nof Terms<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><table class=\\\"MsoTableGrid\\\" border=\\\"1\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border: none;\\\">\\r\\n <tbody><tr>\\r\\n  <td width=\\\"308\\\" valign=\\\"top\\\" style=\\\"width:231.05pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\\r\\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\\\">\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\n  normal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\r\\n  color:red\\\">Analyse<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/td>\\r\\n  <td width=\\\"308\\\" valign=\\\"top\\\" style=\\\"width:231.05pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\\r\\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\\r\\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\\\">\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\n  normal\\\">You will need to examine the topic in detail.&nbsp; Exploring the meaning, covering essential\\r\\n  features and their significance.&nbsp; This\\r\\n  often requires providing more than one perspective on the topic.<\\/p>\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\n  normal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p>\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\\r\\n  normal\\\">Therefore you should make your statement, explain the importance of\\r\\n  this practice and then consider the consequences of not following the good\\r\\n  practices through.&nbsp; This will allow you\\r\\n  to show a well rounded knowledge of the question.<\\/p>\\r\\n  <p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"m