(288, 140, 28, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hi Linda, <\\/p><p>I\'m struggling with this question about the theories and development of frameworks. I feel its staring me in the face but I\'m finding it difficult to&nbsp;write the answer down.<\\/p><p>My understanding is that I need to look at the theories then and describe the practices that are in place now ? Is that correct ? <\\/p><p>Thanks<\\/p><p>Lizzie<br><\\/p>\"}', 1517842291, 1, 0, 0),
