Wingdings\\\">\\u00d8<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/span><!--[endif]--><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\">When\\r\\nyou have resubmitted your work again for marking, (if indeed necessary to do\\r\\nso) you will be sent a new \\u2018Feedback Form\\u2019.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\\" style=\\\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\\\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\\\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nWingdings\\\">\\u00d8<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\\\">Please\\r\\nalways save a copy of your \\u2018Feedback Forms\\u2019 for your own reference.<\\/span><\\/b><b><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\"><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\">If you\\r\\nhave any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact me<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\">Regards<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:Mistral;\\r\\ncolor:#0070C0\\\">Linda Broome-Smith<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNoSpacing\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:red\\\">NCC \\u2013 Support Tutor<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p>\"}', 1517934635, 1, 0, 0),
(308, 28, 129, '{\"Message\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Hello Rhiannon<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">I am about to send you some advice notes to help you with\\r\\nyour studies;<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">I have to send them as separate messages I am afraid, as the\\r\\nsystem will not let me send attachments to email<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Please let me know you received them all - you should get\\r\\nthe following:<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Advice on answering your questions<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">A Glossary of Terms<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Advice on referencing and creating bibliographies<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Advice on reading through your Feedback forms<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Regards<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Linda<\\/p>\"}', 1517934740, 1, 0, 0),
(309, 28, 129, '{\"Message\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" align=\\\"center\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">Advice for\\r\\nanswering your course questions effectively<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" align=\\\"center\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p><span style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">In your studies, you will be challenged to show your\\r\\nknowledge and understanding of particular topics in the form of questions to\\r\\nanswer.&nbsp; <\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Whilst answering the criteria, you will need to provide evidence\\r\\nof your knowledge and understanding of the topic set.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">In order to challenge you in this way, the criteria are\\r\\nworded in particular ways, and it is extremely important that you present your\\r\\nevidence in the particular way it has been set.&nbsp;\\r\\nIf you do not, you might find that your work is referred back to you due\\r\\nto the answer not being fully met in the way it was asked to be presented.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Please have a look at the tips provided below, and also look\\r\\nthrough the <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018Glossary\\r\\nof Terms\\u2019<\\/span><\\/b> that I have also sent, in order to help you to understand\\r\\nthe ways in which the questions should be answered.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">If you need any further help, please do not hesitate to ask\\r\\nme.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\\r\\n id=\\\"_x0000_t75\\\" coordsize=\\\"21600,21600\\\" o:spt=\\\"75\\\" o:preferrelative=\\\"t\\\"\\r\\n path=\\\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\\\" filled=\\\"f\\\" stroked=\\\"f\\\">\\r\\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\\\"miter\\\"\\/>\\r\\n <v:formulas>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"sum @0 1 0\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"sum 0 0 @1\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"prod @2 1 2\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"sum @0 0 1\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"prod @6 1 2\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"sum @8 21600 0\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\\\"\\/>\\r\\n  <v:f eqn=\\\"sum @10 21600 0\\\"\\/>\\r\\n <\\/v:formulas>\\r\\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\\\"f\\\" gradientshapeok=\\\"t\\\" o:connecttype=\\\"rect\\\"\\/>\\r\\n <o:lock v:ext=\\\"edit\\\" aspectratio=\\\"t\\\"\\/>\\r\\n<\\/v:shapetype><v:shape id=\\\"Picture_x0020_0\\\" o:spid=\\\"_x0000_i1025\\\" type=\\\"#_x0000_t75\\\"\\r\\n alt=\\\"helpful tips.jpg\\\" style=\'width:86.25pt;height:85.5pt;visibility:visible;\\r\\n mso-wrap-style:square\'>\\r\\n <v:imagedata src=\\\"file:\\/\\/\\/C:\\\\Users\\\\HRS\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Temp\\\\msohtmlclip1\\\\01\\\\clip_image001.jpg\\\"\\r\\n  o:title=\\\"helpful tips\\\"\\/>\\r\\n<\\/v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\\\"115\\\" height=\\\"114\\\" src=\\\"file:\\/\\/\\/C:\\/Users\\/HRS\\/AppData\\/Local\\/Temp\\/msohtmlclip1\\/01\\/clip_image002.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"helpful tips.jpg\\\" v:shapes=\\\"Picture_x0020_0\\\"><!--[endif]--><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">#1 -<\\/span><\\/b> Before you\\r\\ntry to answer any questions <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018ALWAYS\\u2019<\\/span><\\/b> read the question fully and carefully\\r\\nat least <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">twice<\\/span><\\/b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">.<\\/span> Take your time to be sure exactly what is being\\r\\nasked of you. <\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">#2-<\\/span><\\/b> The first\\r\\nword of the criteria question explains in which way the question should be\\r\\nanswered.&nbsp; This verb is very important in\\r\\norder to understand the way in which the question needs to be answered.&nbsp; Please refer to the <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018Glossary of Terms\\u2019<\\/span><\\/b> that I have\\r\\nsent through to you, in order to fully explain this.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">#3 -<\\/span><\\/b> After you\\r\\nread through the question twice, it could be helpful for you to <span style=\\\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\\\">highlight<\\/span> the <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">FIRST <\\/span><\\/b>word,\\r\\nand then underline all the important features of the question.&nbsp; Then you can focus on these words throughout\\r\\nyour answer and also remind yourself not to miss them out.&nbsp; For example:<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b>\\u201c<span style=\\\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\\\">Explain<\\/span> the <u>importance<\\/u>\\r\\nof <u>reflecting<\\/u> practice in <u>continuously<\\/u> improving the quality of\\r\\nservice.\\u201d<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Your answer therefore would not be just as statement of what\\r\\nreflection is, but why it is such an important skill to use, and why it should\\r\\nbe a continuous practice in order to improve service. <\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">#4 -<\\/span><\\/b> Some\\r\\nquestions may ask you for a <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018Range\\u2019 <\\/span><\\/b>of ideas.&nbsp; When the word <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018Range\\u2019<\\/span><\\/b> appears in the criteria\\r\\nquestion, you must give at least <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u2018three\\u2019 <\\/span><\\/b>examples for the range to be\\r\\nvalid.&nbsp; You can have as many as you like <b>BUT<\\/b> a minimum of three is required.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">#5-<\\/span><\\/b> Some\\r\\nquestions have more than one part to them.&nbsp;\\r\\nThat is why it is important to read them through at least twice.&nbsp; Some questions will be bullet pointed.&nbsp; In this case you will not be able to fully\\r\\nanswer the question unless all the elements have been addressed.&nbsp; For example;<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">\\u201cExplain what is meant by: <o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\\\" style=\\\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\\\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nSymbol;color:#7030A0\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">Diversity<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1\\\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nSymbol;color:#7030A0\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">Equality<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\\" style=\\\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1\\\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\\r\\nSymbol;color:#7030A0\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">Inclusion<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">In order for you to answer this question fully, all three headings\\r\\nwould have to be used and answered separately.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;color:red\\\">#6 \\u2013<\\/span><\\/b> Don\\u2019t\\r\\nforget that the questions are asking you to show <b><span style=\\\"color:#7030A0\\\">YOUR<\\/span><\\/b> knowledge and\\r\\nunderstanding, not just repeating what your study materials are stating.&nbsp; In order for you to portray your own\\r\\nknowledge and understanding make sure you have done some independent reading\\r\\nand research as well as using the NCC study materials.&nbsp; This will give you perspective in your\\r\\nwork.&