(370, 65, 134, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hi Emma,<\\/p><p>Thank you for resubmitting.<\\/p><p>If the website says you have not been on it then either it has been plagiarised already by another site or worse, it has plagiarised another site. You can see the text you have lifted off it though. Choosing a good, academic source is extremely important for your studies and avoid already plagiarised sites like the plague! It may be that what you have copy and pasted could be on 20 plagiarised sites. This happens all the time.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Obviously I check for plagiarism as it is not lawful for me to sign someone else\'s work off as one of my students. My signature remains on the student\'s certificate so I am very careful about what I accept.<\\/p><p>Kind regards<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Sarah<br><\\/p>\"}', 1518514828, 1, 0, 0),
