(373, 40, 207, '{\"Message\":\"<p>Hi Leah<\\/p><p>Thanks for your message.&nbsp; For Activity 3, you need to complete the 2 itinerary templates at the end of the module.&nbsp; One showing the activities you would do and one showing what the guide would do.&nbsp; You can give an idea of some of the timings - ie what they will do in the morning, afternoon etc.<\\/p><p>Let me know if you have any other questions.<\\/p><p>Best wishes<\\/p><p>Samantha&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', 1518528533, 1, 0, 0),
