(381, 63, 67, '{\"Message\":\"<p>All the information you need is in the module. There are various methods such as interviewing current post holder, sitting and observing etc. If you google job analysis methods you will find a number of sites that will give you this information. However, you only need to give one or two methods that you can use and explain how you will do this, so about half a page text on this one area.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>I hope this helps but please contact me if you have any queries.<\\/p><p>Kind Regards<\\/p><p>Helen<\\/p>\"}', 1518537411, 1, 0, 0),
